BDE

Serves two.

Start with two wine glasses.
Pour two smoked cherries and 1oz smoked cherry syrup into each glass.
Place four ice cubes into each glass.
Shake 12oz cognac and 4oz lemon juice with ice. Split into each glass. Pour sparkling wine over, until nearly full.
Optional: top with a Cointreau float until full.
Garnish with a twist. 
